the duration of the spell lasting a on a 60 warrior with over 100 MR (PVE gear) is to funny, the reaction when it does stick is OMG ROOT STUCK and by the time everyone realizes that it actually DID stick, it is gone.<br>
<br>
that root is just enough time to say wtf...and while getting beat on switch to resist gear before the nukes start coming in.<br>
<br>
yeah i am twinked to hell (BD ear/bracers, vel diamond rings and froggy) all taken off my retired 60 warrior, so this is not for all cases, but at 44 3 SK's couldn't land darkness on me (i dropped the monk before they got me though) and my resists stink compared to a warrior at compareable level, MR especially. my MR is in the 90's with endure magic and full resist gear on at 44 on Kerir<br>
<br>
at 60 i can't remember the last time i got snared or darked on my warrior, rooted for a second or 2....yeah. but without tash or malo cast on him i just laughed and kept on going. <br>
<br>
my resists were laughable compared to guys in Baju and Shadark's guild.<br>
